                                                                           "fontSize":  11,
                                                                           "color":  "#333333",
                                                                           "text":  [
                                                                                        "Contrary to the belief that areca",
                                                                                        "nut and tobacco use are dying",
                                                                                        "traditions confined to the elderly,",
                                                                                        "the data reveals a terrifying",
                                                                                        "trend: the highest prevalence is",
                                                                                        "concentrated in the younger",
                                                                                        "generation. Youth aged 15-19 lead",
                                                                                        "with a 5.9% prevalence, followed",
                                                                                        "closely by young adults aged 20-29",
                                                                                        "at 5.6%. This indicates a fresh",
                                                                                        "wave of addiction among the",
                                                                                        "workforce of tomorrow."
                                                                                    ],
