                                                                           "fontSize":  11,
                                                                           "color":  "#333333",
                                                                           "text":  [
                                                                                        "In a surprising reversal of",
                                                                                        "conventional wisdom that associates",
                                                                                        "quid chewing with remote rural",
                                                                                        "traditions, urban environments",
                                                                                        "exhibit the highest prevalence at a",
                                                                                        "staggering 10.0%. In comparison,",
                                                                                        "rural fringes stand at 3.9%, and",
                                                                                        "remote communities report only",
                                                                                        "2.5%. The urban lifestyle and",
                                                                                        "stress may be modernizing and",
                                                                                        "accelerating these habits."
